00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:17.510
No, no. Meijuan is in danger!

00:15:17.510 --> 00:15:18.000
Meijuan is in danger...

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:19.790
Who is Meijuan? What danger is she in?

00:15:19.790 --> 00:15:20.120
Here.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:21.320
Here you are, Inspector.

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:23.390
M-Meijuan asked me to give you this.

00:15:23.390 --> 00:15:24.120
I'll read it.

00:15:24.750 --> 00:15:25.150
Alright.

00:15:25.150 --> 00:15:26.360
Take a seat. I'll read the note.

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:26.860
Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:26.860 --> 00:15:27.910
Calm down. No rush.

00:15:27.910 --> 00:15:28.320
Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:29.050
Take it easy.

00:15:29.150 --> 00:15:29.510
Meijuan...

00:15:29.510 --> 00:15:30.440
Don't worry. Don't worry.

00:15:30.440 --> 00:15:32.080
-Sit down please.
-Calm down.

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:33.280
Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:33.390 --> 00:15:34.590
Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:36.840
Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:38.480
It's okay. We're here to help.

00:15:38.480 --> 00:15:39.870
Meijuan... Meijuan is in danger.

00:15:39.870 --> 00:15:41.670
Calm down. Put your mind at ease.

00:15:41.670 --> 00:15:43.510
Liu, Yuan, Le!

00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:45.240
Look after her. Let's go!

00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:47.100
Meijuan is in danger. Meijuan...

00:15:55.220 --> 00:15:58.200
[To commemorate the1927 fundraiser
held by the relief commission]

00:16:00.910 --> 00:16:01.860
I never imagined...

00:16:01.860 --> 00:16:02.550
[Fundraising Convention of China
International Famine Relief Commission]

00:16:02.550 --> 00:16:03.480
this would be...

00:16:06.110 --> 00:16:08.300
the last photo of Yongjie.

00:16:14.450 --> 00:16:15.780
Get up. We're in danger.

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:27.870
Officer Lu,

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:29.960
are you okay?

00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:31.880
You're a real jerk!

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:34.720
Yes.

00:16:37.510 --> 00:16:38.510
I am a jerk.

00:16:40.550 --> 00:16:41.910
But I can't be a worse jerk than you are,
can I?

00:16:41.910 --> 00:16:42.770
Come back here!

00:16:43.530 --> 00:16:44.080
Ma'am!

00:16:45.800 --> 00:16:47.260
I'm here to see Meijuan...

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:49.650
I saw everything.

00:16:49.920 --> 00:16:52.250
You pushed your own mother to the ground.

00:16:52.670 --> 00:16:54.240
Since you're unfilial,

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:57.150
I should punish you
in your mother's stead!

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:01.510
So this is why you killed?

00:17:03.120 --> 00:17:04.400
You think you were serving justice?

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:05.200
Exactly!

00:17:06.040 --> 00:17:07.109
Those who mistreat their parents

00:17:07.109 --> 00:17:09.109
don't deserve to live in this world!

00:17:58.200 --> 00:17:58.770
Freeze!

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:01.200
Lu Yizhen.

00:18:01.610 --> 00:18:02.200
Stay still!

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:02.930
Lu Yizhen...

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:40.720
Go away.

00:18:46.450 --> 00:18:47.250
Back off!

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:55.440
Go away!

00:18:57.680 --> 00:18:58.480
It's okay now.

00:18:59.310 --> 00:18:59.970
All is fine.

00:19:01.110 --> 00:19:01.750
I'm here.

00:19:02.790 --> 00:19:03.720
Don't be afraid.

00:19:04.790 --> 00:19:05.720
I'm here for you.

00:19:07.820 --> 00:19:08.680
I'm right here.

00:19:24.640 --> 00:19:25.920
Just now, I...

00:19:27.070 --> 00:19:27.680
So, I...

00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:28.350
I get it.

00:19:31.930 --> 00:19:32.880
Are you alright?

00:19:34.110 --> 00:19:34.830
I'm fine.

00:19:39.400 --> 00:19:40.060
How is Dong?

00:19:40.350 --> 00:19:41.830
He's fine. Don't worry.

00:19:49.960 --> 00:19:50.760
You're awake?

00:19:51.270 --> 00:19:52.000
Dr. Gu.

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:55.640
This is Gu Sinian,
an attending psychiatrist

00:19:55.640 --> 00:19:56.770
at Nianci Hospital.

00:19:57.340 --> 00:19:58.410
Dr. Gu has a good relationship

00:19:58.410 --> 00:19:59.720
with our police station.

00:19:59.720 --> 00:20:01.790
Some officers were traumatized
in the line of duty,

00:20:01.790 --> 00:20:02.990
and Mr. Gu cured them.

00:20:04.090 --> 00:20:04.490
Hello.

00:20:04.490 --> 00:20:05.380
Nice to meet you, Dr. Gu.

00:20:05.380 --> 00:20:06.670
Be seated. It's okay.

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:14.350
Traumatized?

00:20:15.310 --> 00:20:16.830
Because I fired my gun?

00:20:17.830 --> 00:20:19.360
Have a good talk with Dr. Gu.

00:20:19.920 --> 00:20:21.120
Consider it an order.

00:20:21.480 --> 00:20:22.940
I'll wait for you outside.

00:20:25.350 --> 00:20:26.160
Rest assured.

00:20:28.200 --> 00:20:29.750
Let's have a brief chat.

00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:42.350
Judging from your condition,

00:20:42.350 --> 00:20:43.740
I assume you still have a clear mind,

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:45.740
since you remember firing your gun.

00:20:46.400 --> 00:20:48.400
Dr. Gu, I...

00:20:49.500 --> 00:20:51.260
When I was in Fang Ruhai's house,

00:20:51.260 --> 00:20:53.190
I drank some water with drugs in it.

00:20:53.350 --> 00:20:54.270
So, at that time, I might not have been

00:20:54.270 --> 00:20:55.270
of sound mind...

00:20:55.270 --> 00:20:56.070
I understand.

00:20:56.520 --> 00:20:58.160
Inspector Guan already told me

00:20:58.160 --> 00:20:59.360
what happened there.

00:21:04.280 --> 00:21:06.280
How is Fang Ruhai?

00:21:07.240 --> 00:21:08.440
He's in emergency surgery.

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:11.060
It's still unclear
whether he'll make it or not,

00:21:11.060 --> 00:21:13.260
since he was shot in the femoral artery.

00:21:14.350 --> 00:21:15.750
I didn't mean to kill him.

00:21:18.200 --> 00:21:19.210
Do you regret it?

00:21:28.480 --> 00:21:29.000
No.

00:21:31.720 --> 00:21:33.450
I had no other option back then.

00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:34.680
You believe...

00:21:35.880 --> 00:21:37.350
you would've died

00:21:37.440 --> 00:21:39.370
if you hadn't shot him at that time?

00:21:40.110 --> 00:21:40.640
Yes.

00:21:46.550 --> 00:21:48.410
But still, I didn't want him dead.

00:21:50.750 --> 00:21:51.550
I understand.

00:21:53.160 --> 00:21:53.760
Very good.

00:21:56.440 --> 00:21:58.070
You're feeling guilt, remorse,

00:21:58.070 --> 00:22:00.880
even fear, and a sense of dread.

00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:02.930
This is completely normal.

00:22:03.270 --> 00:22:04.110
Your counterattack

00:22:04.110 --> 00:22:06.200
was an instinctive response to stress.

00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:08.030
Though officers such as yourself
have received professional training,

00:22:08.030 --> 00:22:10.880
and are more mentally resilient
than ordinary people,

00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:13.590
the human will to live
can be stronger than you think,

00:22:13.590 --> 00:22:15.590
especially in extreme situations.

00:22:16.030 --> 00:22:17.890
It's fine to have those emotions,

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.450
but don't beat yourself up.

00:22:20.920 --> 00:22:22.200
The will to live...

00:22:27.750 --> 00:22:29.960
Perhaps it's related
to what I've been through.

00:22:29.960 --> 00:22:30.480
I know.

00:22:31.110 --> 00:22:33.000
I read your profile beforehand

00:22:33.440 --> 00:22:35.590
and learned a bit about your past.

00:22:36.310 --> 00:22:37.920
Don't hastily draw conclusions

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:39.400
on uncertain matters.

00:22:40.630 --> 00:22:41.270
But this is not

00:22:41.270 --> 00:22:42.930
a subject of today's session.

00:22:43.920 --> 00:22:46.250
Regarding the shooting incident only...

00:22:47.510 --> 00:22:49.590
would you feel better
if I said the following?

00:22:49.590 --> 00:22:50.320
Here it goes.

00:22:51.000 --> 00:22:53.130
Whether you had shot Fang Ruhai or not,

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:55.200
he wouldn't have lived much longer.

00:22:56.110 --> 00:22:57.040
What do you mean?

00:22:57.440 --> 00:22:58.840
Fang Ruhai was diagnosed

00:22:58.930 --> 00:23:00.720
with a terminal illness a year ago.

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:01.920
He would probably...

00:23:02.460 --> 00:23:04.320
only have a few more weeks to live.

00:23:06.640 --> 00:23:08.300
It's okay. Relax. All is fine.

00:23:09.960 --> 00:23:10.750
Take a break.

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:11.690
Eat an apple.

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:30.750
Dr. Gu,

00:23:30.770 --> 00:23:32.900
don't you have other questions for me?

00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:35.270
No.

00:23:36.070 --> 00:23:37.200
Is the therapy over?

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:38.200
Yes.

00:23:39.590 --> 00:23:40.640
For you,

00:23:41.310 --> 00:23:43.570
this conversation was just a formality.

00:23:44.040 --> 00:23:44.900
You'll be fine.

00:23:45.400 --> 00:23:46.330
Trust yourself.

00:23:56.330 --> 00:24:02.790
[Office]

00:24:34.920 --> 00:24:35.800
How are you?

00:24:42.240 --> 00:24:43.480
I'm quite well.

00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:45.080
You didn't have to wait here.

00:24:47.030 --> 00:24:48.240
I just came to tell you

00:24:48.950 --> 00:24:50.010
the case is closed.

00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:54.160
You can return to your post
when you're discharged from the hospital.

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:55.960
What's the deal with Fang Ruhai?

00:24:59.690 --> 00:25:01.350
Actually, he started killing

00:25:01.660 --> 00:25:03.060
as he became worried that after he died,

00:25:03.060 --> 00:25:05.060
no one would take care of his mother.

00:25:05.590 --> 00:25:07.500
Fang Ruhai's wife passed away early.

00:25:07.500 --> 00:25:09.030
They didn't have children.

00:25:10.030 --> 00:25:11.440
Fang is a rather rigid man

00:25:12.350 --> 00:25:13.880
without any close friends.

00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:16.270
The only solution

00:25:16.310 --> 00:25:17.400
he could come up with

00:25:17.400 --> 00:25:18.590
was to kill his own mother first

00:25:18.590 --> 00:25:20.120
before taking his own life.

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:21.200
That way,

00:25:21.220 --> 00:25:22.960
his mother wouldn't suffer for a lack of

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:23.690
caregivers.

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:29.300
Fang Ruhaiâ€™s mother

00:25:29.300 --> 00:25:30.500
noticed something odd with her son

00:25:30.500 --> 00:25:32.160
and wrote a letter to her good friend,

00:25:32.160 --> 00:25:33.880
namely Mrs. Gao in the nursing home.

00:25:33.880 --> 00:25:35.830
Unfortunately, Mrs. Gao has dementia.

00:25:35.830 --> 00:25:36.750
Although she received the letter,

00:25:36.750 --> 00:25:38.110
she forgot all the content,

00:25:38.110 --> 00:25:40.570
except that she had to go see
her good friend.

00:25:44.400 --> 00:25:45.920
But it was too late.

00:25:47.030 --> 00:25:49.290
Fang Ruhai sedated his mother as planned

00:25:49.680 --> 00:25:51.140
and ended her life at last.

00:25:54.070 --> 00:25:56.200
He already planned to commit suicide.

00:25:56.270 --> 00:25:58.480
What turned him into a serial killer?

00:25:58.810 --> 00:26:00.960
Just when Fang Ruhai
was about to commit suicide,

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:02.290
at a fundraising event,

00:26:02.500 --> 00:26:04.000
he met Liu Jialiang's mother,

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:05.440
who was there to make donations.

00:26:05.440 --> 00:26:06.640
By chance, he learned

00:26:06.650 --> 00:26:09.110
that Liu Jialiang had abused
his own mother.

00:26:10.070 --> 00:26:11.870
That was when Fang Ruhai started

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:13.970
turning into a twisted person.

00:26:14.720 --> 00:26:15.550
I believe

00:26:16.110 --> 00:26:18.440
that after he murdered Liu Jialiang,

00:26:19.190 --> 00:26:20.190
he decided to kill

00:26:21.480 --> 00:26:23.310
as many unfilial children as possible

00:26:23.310 --> 00:26:24.510
before his own death.

00:26:26.200 --> 00:26:28.270
Just based on what he saw
in that brief moment,

00:26:28.270 --> 00:26:30.110
he determined that I was unfilial,

00:26:30.110 --> 00:26:31.170
so he had to kill me?

00:26:34.680 --> 00:26:37.140
Maybe he wasn't like that
in the first place.

00:26:38.070 --> 00:26:39.130
Major life changes

00:26:39.830 --> 00:26:41.560
can impact one's state of mind.

00:26:42.790 --> 00:26:44.320
I assume you know that well.

00:26:48.350 --> 00:26:49.350
What do you mean?

00:26:52.720 --> 00:26:53.520
Let me ask you.

00:26:54.530 --> 00:26:56.930
Why did you want to become
a police officer?

00:27:03.030 --> 00:27:03.680
I guess

00:27:04.200 --> 00:27:07.000
you made up your mind
to find the killer from years ago

00:27:07.000 --> 00:27:08.200
all by yourself.

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.500
So what if that's true?

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:15.330
This is my fault.

00:27:16.510 --> 00:27:17.720
I apologize to you.

00:27:18.730 --> 00:27:20.530
I don't expect you to forgive me,

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:22.920
or to understand my actions.

00:27:23.550 --> 00:27:26.110
I admit I hate the idea
of you working in the police station.

00:27:26.110 --> 00:27:28.640
But if you insist on
continuing with this job,

00:27:31.110 --> 00:27:33.310
don't change yourself
for anyone else.

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:18.370
Juggernaut,

00:28:18.550 --> 00:28:20.710
will the murderer
be identified in the end?

00:28:20.710 --> 00:28:23.110
So far,
Jie seems to be the biggest suspect.

00:28:23.200 --> 00:28:24.960
But there may be a twist.

00:28:25.130 --> 00:28:27.130
The cleaner could also be a suspect.

00:28:31.240 --> 00:28:33.370
Just keep reading and you'll find out.

00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:36.070
The murderer isn't Jie,

00:28:36.070 --> 00:28:37.240
but his girlfriend.

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:39.510
It's indicated at the end of chapter two.

00:28:39.510 --> 00:28:40.240
Juggernaut,

00:28:40.350 --> 00:28:42.960
are we thinking the same way?

00:28:43.350 --> 00:28:45.200
Another murder case with no blood.

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:47.530
Juggernaut does have a consistent style.

00:29:26.350 --> 00:29:28.140
Thank you for saving me
in Fang Ruhai's case.

00:29:28.140 --> 00:29:29.800
It was you who saved yourself.

00:29:30.070 --> 00:29:31.370
But I get to work
in the Police Station...

00:29:31.370 --> 00:29:32.270
That decision was made by the higher-ups,

00:29:32.270 --> 00:29:33.070
not me.

00:29:36.440 --> 00:29:37.110
The Police Station is a place

00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:38.680
that values individual ability.

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:39.940
If you don't think
you're suited for this place,

00:29:39.940 --> 00:29:41.510
you may apply to be transferred back
to Inspector Zhu's team

00:29:41.510 --> 00:29:43.140
and resume your old job
of buying breakfast

00:29:43.140 --> 00:29:44.670
and doing archival search.

00:29:45.160 --> 00:29:47.020
Don't ever expect me to thank you.

00:29:49.480 --> 00:29:50.550
You're overthinking it.

00:29:50.550 --> 00:29:51.030
As you're working here,

00:29:51.030 --> 00:29:52.350
I have only one requirement for you.

00:29:52.350 --> 00:29:53.750
That is to obey my orders.

00:29:56.350 --> 00:29:57.720
Now, go buy me breakfast.

00:29:57.720 --> 00:29:58.590
What?

00:30:00.270 --> 00:30:01.200
Are you serious?

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:02.030
Of course.

00:30:02.400 --> 00:30:03.800
Do I look like I'm joking?

00:30:03.830 --> 00:30:04.890
Buy me some pan-fried buns

00:30:04.890 --> 00:30:05.890
with crispy skin,

00:30:05.920 --> 00:30:07.450
plus a bowl of tofu pudding.

00:30:15.090 --> 00:30:16.560
What's so good
about the Police Station?

00:30:16.560 --> 00:30:19.020
I still have to tofu pudding
for my boss here.

00:30:27.110 --> 00:30:27.790
Inspector.

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:31.690
He's waited a long time for you.

00:30:32.480 --> 00:30:33.160
Got it.

00:30:35.400 --> 00:30:36.200
Director Huo.

00:30:38.240 --> 00:30:40.160
I've transferred an officer
to your unit.

00:30:40.160 --> 00:30:40.960
Thank you, Director Huo,

00:30:40.960 --> 00:30:43.360
for adding manpower
to the Police Station.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:46.000
This is the only place

00:30:46.030 --> 00:30:48.490
where Lu's potential
can be fully realized.

00:30:48.580 --> 00:30:49.580
What's your plan?

00:30:50.680 --> 00:30:52.000
I'll give her chances to use her strengths

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:53.440
during case investigations.

00:30:53.440 --> 00:30:54.510
I promise to help her live up

00:30:54.510 --> 00:30:56.970
to your expectations for her,
Director Huo.

00:30:58.200 --> 00:30:58.920
Really?

00:30:59.840 --> 00:31:01.820
Don't think I'm clueless.

00:31:01.940 --> 00:31:04.440
You're working on that old case again,
aren't you?

00:31:04.440 --> 00:31:05.880
The suspect of that case

00:31:06.160 --> 00:31:08.890
from years ago already vanished
without a trace.

00:31:09.060 --> 00:31:10.990
Even the only survivor, Lu Yizhen,

00:31:11.030 --> 00:31:11.960
can't remember anything.

00:31:11.960 --> 00:31:13.000
She lost her memory!

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:14.720
What leads do you have? How to proceed?

00:31:14.720 --> 00:31:17.160
That gang must be still doing
the same old evil stuff.

00:31:17.160 --> 00:31:19.490
It's just what you say. Where's the proof?

00:31:20.440 --> 00:31:21.510
Word has it

00:31:21.830 --> 00:31:24.350
that the mastermind
behind this human trafficking case, Ghost,

00:31:24.350 --> 00:31:26.480
has recently reappeared in Shanghai.

00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:28.110
Ghost?

00:31:28.440 --> 00:31:29.840
Didn't he flee Shanghai?

00:31:31.720 --> 00:31:32.720
An informant said

00:31:33.200 --> 00:31:35.460
the fire back then
was exactly caused by Ghost.

00:31:35.460 --> 00:31:36.980
It was that very fire

00:31:37.550 --> 00:31:39.680
that brought Lu Yizhen's case to light.

00:31:39.680 --> 00:31:42.030
Nobody saw Ghost again after the fire.

00:31:43.350 --> 00:31:45.440
People all thought he had fled Shanghai.

00:31:45.440 --> 00:31:46.510
But a source claimed

00:31:46.510 --> 00:31:47.590
to have seen Ghost in Shanghai lately.

00:31:47.590 --> 00:31:48.990
And it's highly possible

00:31:49.240 --> 00:31:50.920
that Ghost has never left the city
all this time.

00:31:50.920 --> 00:31:51.980
That can't be true.

00:31:53.110 --> 00:31:55.510
If he never left Shanghai,

00:31:55.660 --> 00:31:57.030
we would have found him already!

00:31:57.030 --> 00:31:59.440
What if
he's been concealing his real identity

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:01.500
and has cut ties with all his fellows?

00:32:01.750 --> 00:32:03.280
We wouldn't know, would we?

00:32:05.200 --> 00:32:06.730
I suppose that's possible.

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:09.030
I've also heard

00:32:09.200 --> 00:32:10.660
that he was once put in jail

00:32:10.720 --> 00:32:12.160
under a different identity.

00:32:12.160 --> 00:32:14.020
That was why we couldn't find him.

00:32:14.790 --> 00:32:17.350
He's got some nerve.

00:32:17.960 --> 00:32:19.960
Sometimes the most dangerous place

00:32:20.270 --> 00:32:21.400
is the safest place.

00:32:24.110 --> 00:32:26.110
Oh, Guan Cen,

00:32:27.130 --> 00:32:29.990
you've been quite busy
behind my back, haven't you?

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:33.580
I need to give myself closure.

00:32:34.890 --> 00:32:35.860
What closure?

00:32:39.270 --> 00:32:40.600
What are you doing here?

00:32:42.030 --> 00:32:43.550
I was worried
that your breakfast might get cold

00:32:43.550 --> 00:32:45.310
before you ate it, so I brought it over.

00:32:45.310 --> 00:32:47.970
I just overheard your conversation
by the door.

00:32:49.950 --> 00:32:52.010
You're investigating that old case?

00:32:53.070 --> 00:32:53.790
Didn't I make it clear

00:32:53.790 --> 00:32:54.970
to you at the entrance just now?

00:32:54.970 --> 00:32:55.830
I have only one requirement for you

00:32:55.830 --> 00:32:57.680
as you work in the Police Station.

00:32:57.680 --> 00:32:59.080
That is to obey my orders.

00:32:59.590 --> 00:33:00.830
Sharing the superior's burden

00:33:00.830 --> 00:33:02.070
is also part of my job.

00:33:02.550 --> 00:33:03.950
Am I right, Director Huo?

00:33:06.640 --> 00:33:08.220
Since Ghost is in Shanghai,

00:33:08.250 --> 00:33:09.980
he has to interact with others.

00:33:10.590 --> 00:33:12.480
Maybe we'll have useful findings

00:33:12.530 --> 00:33:14.350
if we visit the place
where the informant saw Ghost

00:33:14.350 --> 00:33:16.350
and ask around in the neighborhood.

00:33:20.920 --> 00:33:23.310
Looks like Inspector Guan and I
have the same idea.

00:33:23.310 --> 00:33:24.130
That being the case,

00:33:24.130 --> 00:33:25.730
I request to join the investigation.

00:33:25.730 --> 00:33:26.300
No way.

00:33:34.200 --> 00:33:34.960
Then forget I was

00:33:34.960 --> 00:33:36.420
ever in this office today.

00:33:36.880 --> 00:33:37.640
Lu Yizhen.

00:33:40.240 --> 00:33:41.240
What do you want?

00:33:44.030 --> 00:33:45.490
Do you really want to join?

00:33:45.570 --> 00:33:46.240
Yes.